# vercel_project (Data Source)

Project DataSource

## Example Usage

```terraform
data "vercel_project" "my_project" {
  id      = "320f70a5-902f-4ce9-b659-240cd9bb1d5f"
  slug    = "...my_slug..."
  team_id = "...my_team_id..."
}
```
